    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/818134962832293888",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/818134962832293888",
      "title": "A cartoon for Guardian Books ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s640x960/762afbbcc98e66c37ae8c30882b269b18afae8bb.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"848\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Panel 1 Caption: The town is famed for its year-round book festival, but for one weekend in summer, it closes.  The literary people leave on a fleet of coaches and the tents are dismantled.  Image: Workers take down a tent. A bus departs.  Panel 2 Caption: The unbroken parade of bookshops on the high street move novels and tote bags to back rooms and fill their shelves with everyday items   Image: A bookshop with shelves containing eggs, loo roll, a coffee pot, a bucket, bleach, a pineapple, etc  Panel 3 Caption: With no talks, signings, or workshops to attend, the townsfolk gather on the green, conversing uncertainly on non-literary topics.   Image: people on the green with speech bubbles labelled &quot;The weather&quot;, &quot;Football&quot;, and &quot;Proposed Ring-road&quot;  Panel 4 Caption: Everyone enjoys the novelty, but agrees that one weekend is enough. On Monday morning the festival resumes with a kev-note address from Robert Macfarlane.  Image: A fascinated audience watches Robert talk, a projector shows a book with a bird on the cover.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s75x75_c1/6c5be8afc6ac36b0c323516d729cdb69a021ac49.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s100x200/75236ec448cb6bafa2c1051a5b83cdf741edeb3d.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s250x400/44222175de8f9cc87533964a92ef599d618aff4b.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s400x600/e1eb7af5e1113d3d28cafbec60297eb245cc9abb.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s500x750/2de8bb124a7e0309b071b533f8cd49d0aa933d32.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s540x810/849701b50f86d5ba0cb19a9eac170cc596148acf.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s640x960/762afbbcc98e66c37ae8c30882b269b18afae8bb.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s1280x1920/c546a42a8ccf13780eeb718d06a02073d5bf5f8a.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/77992406feccb6da6f65accbc4def845/0c26b6d575d36a75-0f/s2048x3072/ede11f7026527eda8a88ee895651c53ca1c0a1a7.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
